<p>Where on Earth is Szeged? Does it even have an airport? (No.) Why go this far for a Drupal event? The exact same questions have been asked by people when they were thinking about coming to <a href="http://szeged2008.drupalcon.org/">DrupalCon Szeged in 2008</a>. Here are some quotes from after that event:</p>
<ul>
<li><em>”The team who ran this Drupalcon just rocked the socks off!”</em> - @add1sun, Lullabot</li>
<li><em>”Had one hell of a blast at the drupalcon in Szeged”</em> - @mortendk, Geek Royale</li>
<li><em>”Most Geek-Rawkin-Awesome DrupalCon! Szeged rulez OK! Thanks to all who made it so great!”</em> - @horncologne, Acquia</li>
